<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ConUHacks 9 – Project Preview</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        /* Full-page styling */
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
            background: url('/assets/conuhacks-banner.png') no-repeat center;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }

        /* Semi-transparent overlay for better readability */
        .overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .container {
            margin-left: 0;
            margin-right: 0;
            position: relative;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 30px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); /* Subtle white background */
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #800000; /* Concordia Burgundy */
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #333;
        }

        .notice {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #800000; /* Concordia Burgundy */
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #a00000;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="overlay"></div>
<div class="container">
    <h1>ConUHacks 9 – Project Preview</h1>
    <p class="notice">This page is currently under development.</p>
    <p>Our project is part of ConUHacks 9. Additional features and improvements will be available depending on the outcome.</p>
    <p>Stay tuned for updates.</p>
    <a href="/" class="button">Return to Home</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>
